highlights.text: “Solid (feat. Drake)” by Young Stoner Life, Young Thug, Gunna, and Drake is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #27.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 220 weeks straight.
Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Peaches (feat. Daniel Caesar & Giveon)” is the highest at #2.
“Levitating” by Dua Lipa is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 87 spots at #95.
